        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Tesla 全新 Model 3 Performance 接受订购   Elon Musk：快过保时捷 911</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/24/new-tesla-model-3-performance/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=new-tesla-model-3-performance</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/24/new-tesla-model-3-performance/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 05:32:37 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla Model 3]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla Model 3 Performance]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1231061</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">Tesla 宣布今日推出 Model 3 Performance，现已于 Tesla 官方网站接受订购，「一换一」计划后价格为 HK$396,880。Elon Musk 早前更在 X（前称 Twitter）表示，新 Model 3 Performance 比保时捷 911 更快。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231063" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/436945581_4055703190-694x455.png" alt="" width="694" height="455" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/436945581_4055703190-694x455.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/436945581_4055703190.png 1206w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Model 3 Performance 是 Model 3 的升级版本，无论里外均有不少升级，以配合「Ludicrous」高性能模式。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231067" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_59-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_59-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_59-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Ludicrous 模式曾在 2016 至 2021 年间生产的 Model S 及 Model X Performance 版本中提供。Model 3 Performance 使用最新的技术，仅需 3.1 秒即可由静止起步加速至时速 100 公里，并在单次充电下提供 528 公里续航距离（WLTP）。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231068" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_52-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_52-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_52-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Model 3 Performance 配备带有 Ludicrous 标志的全新前座椅、全新且更大的后尾翼，以及全新的自动适应减震系统，以增强整体驾驶体验。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231069" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_64-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_64-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_64-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲带有 Ludicrous 标志的全新前座椅</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231070" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_83-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_83-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_83-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲全新且更大的后尾翼</p><p>Model 3 Performance 配备了新的运动型座椅。新座椅支撑力更强，而且形状和结构在转弯和动态驾驶过程中可以提供更多侧向支撑之余，亦保持日常驾驶的便利性和舒适性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231074" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_92-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_92-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_92-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231075" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_93-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_93-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_93-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><div class="block block-layout-builder block-inline-blockrich-text"></div><div></div><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231080" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_91-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_91-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_91-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231076" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_60-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_60-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_60-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231077" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_88-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_88-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_88-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231078" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_89-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_89-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/model3performance_89-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy"